210
00:11:21,748 --> 00:11:24,291
and it's all about the run.

211
00:11:54,097 --> 00:11:58,433
"Don't forget to give yourself
plenty of positive reinforcement."

212
00:11:59,578 --> 00:12:01,773
This is gonna be
your best run yet.

213
00:12:02,816 --> 00:12:06,043
You're going to accomplish
all of your goals.

214
00:12:06,815 --> 00:12:09,533
You are a robot sent
from the future

215
00:12:09,545 --> 00:12:11,553
to win the marathon!

216
00:12:12,796 --> 00:12:15,603
You are... Marshall.

217
00:12:16,238 --> 00:12:19,393
You are... Marshall.

218
00:12:19,437 --> 00:12:23,603
You are Marshall! Yeah!

219
00:12:29,236 --> 00:12:32,851
"Chafing or blisters can
occur in a number of areas,

220
00:12:32,867 --> 00:12:36,481
